products.title: Linear Stem Papaya  Roller Blind
products.description: Add some vibrancy and style to your life with this striking linear stem papaya roller blind. A mix of iconic orla kiely pattern with a bright orange hue could be just what your home has been looking for. Practical as well as stylish this blind is easy to raise and lower while the add some vibrancy and style to your life with this striking linear stem papaya roller blind.
